    installed to. So we can support more hardware for DRBL clients.
  * Changed the default option for client's kernel arch to the same as 
    server for Debian.

 -- Steven Shiau <steven@nchc.org.tw>  Wed, 17 Oct 2012 22:00:39 +0800

